.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, classical, jazz, trance, blues
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, helicopter, bus, jet-ski
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the english is the person who likes red
2. the spanish is the owner of the dog
3. the person driving the taxi is the person who likes green
4. the ukranian is the person driving the skateboard
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the fan of disco is the owner of the snails
7. the fan of classical is the person who likes yellow
8. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the fan of classical is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the fan of trance is the person driving the bus
13. the japanese is the fan of blues
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Transport	|     jet-ski	|      skateboard	|      helicopter	| bus	|     taxi	|
| Music-Genre		|     classical	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| trance	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
